Package: LINEMAP
Title: Lineage Map Simulation and Phylogenetic Tree Construction
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("LINEMAP", "Authors", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "your.email@example.com")
    )
Description: Simulates cell lineage histories with guide-RNA barcode dynamics,
    builds phylogenetic trees from simulated edge tables, and provides helpers
    for plotting and subtree sampling. Example transition data are included.
